" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7dd4b6be800b5627c5a578db88652896cededd7","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:22:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17d90345d63e928129b453b16e53e9d355952373","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a98dc358bd0b84fc98cf12db5bc2b1ac0aa49c71","tid":1373793,"uid":87625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:22:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d80941cd7e02bf0f26f6fa78aa7b1e32b0a50e4","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b9437db1957ac8d546d8c30ec248dad66d770e9","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:22:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be0e4fee8f06004d0125e4f44f3e4704031bd4cf","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a587c6364493897490dbf03bd1e4205c2f1212a7","tid":1373793,"uid":286259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:03.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"0bde0c3141f0683750e78e3412e270c32b0bab83","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"daa45dc724ee6cd26ffb343b498ef7658ef994ff","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fe77363c8474ced8b990e07c1ecd53f6c1e0fd4","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0f04cc2ce9296789b65854d59bf915019ac1c02","tid":1373793,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位<br />\n有關撤唔撤一事<br />\n<br />\n其實出得去既人 多數都係睇tg而唔會上連登（因為啲消息直接好多）（有巴打講可以設旗手）<br />\n<br />\n有時候人多 留低仲安全過撤<br />\n所以一路都話留比現場決定<br />\n<br />\n係屋企既巴打而又真係想幫手既<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣</span> 係ig fb 以至連登share 濫暴片段同post<br />\n2.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫手plan 或者搵邊到有路走</span> 好多時封哂路車改道等等 現場巴打未必有時間check<br />\n<br />\n唔好一昧開post 叫人走叫人走<br />\n而抹殺左成班義士企咁耐 做咁耐野仲要比人打既犧牲<br />\n<br />\n點解我地可以行到依步？<br />\n因為我地<span style=\"color: red;\">行動 同文宣配合</span><br />\n<br />\n唔該咁多位巴打 你地唔係冷氣軍師<br />\n希望係屋企既你地可以每次借黑警濫暴 警黑黎spread out 啲新聞 <span style=\"color: red;\">將香港既事推上國際 咁樣政府先會有壓力 咁樣其他市民先會支持甚至參與</span><br />\n<br />\n你諗下點解依個禮拜咁多市民show 證？<br />\n因為上星期文宣講無差別殺人<br />\n<br />\n所以你地既文宣 講返件事<br />\n真係好重要好重要<br />\n<br />\n唔係就好似721上環開槍咁 無人知 無人理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry 可能 1999 <br />\n但真係唔想白費前線努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"579c928a493847fe6fbaabbf0f603364cc023c42","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4f403dec02f5f32f91c327c44cc94f4bf8be0fe","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6880e9e517750fb3a740b64089d79d01b33b8fda","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bff6e57b36a851a7f5ab9605f4c67475f64f93b9","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a115fe4e6a133d36f3a5913db0ee32e524a6f85","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0d18c9efa9746d236e6430b4e131e81aa921395","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ab2c5e2ef6335b6373c124ef668629037b89508","tid":1373793,"uid":158524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3756d0927c9464db49a4667e73cdbe71